\\n /andrewbranch\\n /apps/copilot-swe-agent\\n /Andarist\\n\\n 38 stars today\\n\\n## [trycua /\\n\\n cua](/trycua/cua)\\n\\n Open-source infrastructure for Computer-Use Agents. Sandboxes, SDKs, and benchmarks to train and evaluate AI agents that can control full desktops (macOS, Linux, Windows).\\n\\n HTML\\n\\n [14,293](/trycua/cua/stargazers)\\n [891](/trycua/cua/forks)\\n\\n Built by\\n\\n /ddupont808\\n /f-trycua\\n /apps/github-actions\\n /jamesmurdza\\n /claude\\n\\n 204 stars today\\n\\n## [gastownhall /\\n\\n beads](/gastownhall/beads)\\n\\n Beads - A memory upgrade for your coding agent\\n\\n## [curl /\\n\\n curl](/curl/curl)\\n\\n A command line tool and library for transferring data with URL syntax, supporting DICT, FILE, FTP, FTPS, GOPHER, GOPHERS, HTTP, HTTPS, IMAP, IMAPS, LDAP, LDAPS, MQTT, MQTTS, POP3, POP3S, RTMP, RTMPS, RTSP, SCP, SFTP, SMB, SMBS, SMTP, SMTPS, TELNET, TFTP, WS and WSS. libcurl offers a myriad of powerful features\\n\\n## [home-assistant /\\n\\n core](/home-assistant/core)\\n\\n 🏡 Open source home automation that puts local control and privacy first.\\n\\n## [codecrafters-io /\\n\\n build-your-own-x](/codecrafters-io/build-your-own-x)\\n\\n Master programming by recreating your favorite technologies from scratch.\\n\\n## [openclaw /\\n\\n openclaw](/openclaw/openclaw)\\n\\n Your own personal AI assistant. Any OS. Any Platform. The lobster way. 🦞\\n\\n## [ComposioHQ /\\n\\n awesome-codex-skills](/ComposioHQ/awesome-codex-skills)\\n\\n A curated list of practical Codex skills for automating workflows across the Codex CLI and API.\\n\\n Python\\n\\n [1,868](/ComposioHQ/awesome-codex-skills/stargazers)\\n [155](/ComposioHQ/awesome-codex-skills/forks)\\n\\n Built by\\n\\n /Prat011\\n /smorky850612\\n /hyhmrright\\n /connerlambden\\n /ProfessorManhattan\\n\\n 518 stars today\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a87b9f9df82150d\\\">>>\"\n}"}],"details":{"url":"https://github.com/trending","finalUrl":"https://github.com/trending","s